n. It allows you to perform basic actions on multiple resources or elements. More information can be found here: https://docs.modx.com/extras/revo/batcher\n\n== REQUIREMENTS ==\n> MODx Revolution 2.0.0-RC-2 or later\n> PHP5 or later\n\n== DOWNLOAD ==\nIt can be downloaded from within the MODX Revolution manager via Package Management, or from the MODX Extras Repository, here: https://rtfm.modx.com/extras/revo/batcher\n\n== USAGE ==\nAfter installing, simply reload the page, and the \'Batcher\' menu option should be available through the top Extras menu.\n\n== HISTORY ==\nBatcher was written by Shaun McCormick as a simple search Extra, and first released on June 2nd, 2010. It is now developed and maintained by Sterc at https://github.com/Sterc/Batcher\n\n== BUGS AND FEATURE REQUESTS ==\nWe greatly value your feedback, feature requests and bug reports. Please issue them on GitHub (https://github.com/Sterc/Batcher/issues/new).\";s:9:\"changelog\";s:1212:\"---------------------\nChangelog for Batcher\n---------------------\nBatcher 2.0.0\n================================================================\n- Added advanced filter option to Resources tab\n- Added empty value to template filter combobox\n- Added filter by context\n- Templates tab is replaced by Elements tab\n- Added Dutch translation\n- Removed functionality to change TV values\n\nBatcher 1.2.0\n================================================================\n- Fixes for MODX 2.2\n\nBatcher 1.1.1\n================================================================\n- Fixes for MODX 2.1\n\nBatcher 1.1.0\n================================================================\n- Added fix for bug with Firefox and batch editing\n- Updated Russian translation\n- Added batch change TV default values for a Template\n- Added batch change TV values for all Resources in a Template\n- Added batch change Template category\n\nBatcher 1.0.1\n================================================================\n- Fixed bug with changeDates due to Revo RC-3 changes\n- Added German translation\n- Added French translation\n\nBatcher 1.0.0\n================================================================\n- Added Russian translation\n- Initial commit\";s:13:\"setup-options\";s:34:\"batcher-2.0.0-pl/setup-options.php\";s:9:\"signature\";s:16:\"batcher-2.0.0-pl\";s:9:\"user_name\";s:0:\"\";s:10:\"user_email\";s:0:\"\";s:6:\"action\";s:26:\"workspace/packages/install\";s:8:\"register\";s:3:\"mgr\";s:5:\"topic\";s:44:\"/workspace/package/install/batcher-2.0.0-pl/\";s:14:\"package_action\";i:0;}', 'Batcher', 'a:38:{s:2:\"id\";s:24:\"5902d543bc8dd3b3788b4567\";s:7:\"package\";s:24:\"4d556cb9b2b083396d000da6\";s:12:\"display_name\";s:16:\"batcher-2.0.0-pl\";s:4:\"name\";s:7:\"Batcher\";s:7:\"version\";s:5:\"2.0.0\";s:13:\"version_major\";s:1:\"2\";s:13:\"version_minor\";s:1:\"0\";s:13:\"version_patch\";s:1:\"0\";s:7:\"release\";s:2:\"pl\";s:8:\"vrelease\";s:2:\"pl\";s:14:\"vrelease_index\";s:0:\"\";s:6:\"author\";s:5:\"sterc\";s:11:\"description\";s:448:\"<p>Batcher is a batch-editing Extra for MODX Revolution. It allows you to perform powerful actions on multiple resources, in order to save you some time.</p><p>More info available at <a href=\"https://www.sterc.nl/en/modx-extras/batcher\" title=\"\" target=\"\">sterc.nl/en/modx-extras/batcher</a></p><p>Please see the official documentation at:&nbsp;<a href=\"http://rtfm.modx.com/display/ADDON/Batcher\">http://rtfm.modx.com/display/ADDON/Batcher</a></p>\";s:12:\"instructions\";s:38:\"<p>Install via Package Management.</p>\";s:9:\"changelog\";s:760:\"<p></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 15px; \"><b>New in 2.0.0</b></p><p><ul><li>An advanced filter option is added to the Resources tab</li><li>An empty value is added to the template filter combobox</li><li>Content filtering is now possible</li><li>The Templates tab is replaced by the Elements tab</li><li>The functionality to change TV values is removed</li><li>Dutch translation was added</li></ul></p><p style=\"m